  "description": "Variation of condition 2 (hours of opening) and condition 7 (delivering restrictions) attached to planning permission ref 2020/3316 dated 17-06-2021 for the change of use to a Cafe (Use Class E) with replacement shopfront and rear extraction flue.The variation would allow opening hours and deliveries between hours of 08:00-23:00 Monday to Thursday, Sundays and Bank Holidays and 08:00-02:00 on Friday and Saturday.",
  "subdivision_of_building": null,
  "actual_completion_date": null,
